<P>
FOG; TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- NORTHERN CALIFORNIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122689-0088 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 153784 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 26, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
