<P>
ENGLAND -- CULTURE; HOLIDAYS; TRADITION; CHRISTMAS; CELEBRATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122689-0098 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 153812 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 26, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
